data.description: This gorgeous home in the sought-after Hollywood Park has so much to offer.  It can be 4 bedrooms, gameroom and study or could be used as a 5 or 6 bedroom home..you decide!  The plan is very versatile! There is a secondary bedroom downstairs that could be used as a second primary! Large treed yard with huge covered patio, and storage shed (approx 12x16); Side entry oversized garage; Roof replaced and just completed end of Sept 2023; siding replaced Sept 2023; Remodeled kitchen with white veined quartz counters with custom cabinets.  Custom touches thruout in the baths!  Wait until you see the primary closet...great storage! Epoxy floored garage! Updated electric panel;  Updated windows..Show and sell!
